title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAY-01-2014 THURS
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAY-01-2014 THURS...PODCAST


The Glenn Beck Program


The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program 5/01/14Thursday, May 01, 2014 12:27 PM



Glenn talks with callers about which states have the happiest people

                     as well as the good and bad about individuals' home states,


 Greg Brannon joins the program to discuss the North Carolina Senate race,

     and Glenn wonders about the Washington Redskins becoming the next target
          for the PC police. 

   Also, the White House continues to boldly lie about Benghazi 
         and few in the media seem to care. 


                 That and more on The Glenn Beck Program!
